{
  "title": "graph2otel: Entra ID compliance overview",
  "uid": "graph2otel-entra-compliance",
  "description": "Entra ID directory hygiene, licensing, credential expiry, CA/PIM posture, secure score, MFA, and risk \u2014 built from graph2otel's entra.* metrics (M2). See top panel for the OTLP-to-Prometheus naming caveat.",
  "tags": [
    "graph2otel",
    "entra"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "refresh": "5m",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "label": "Data source",
        "refresh": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "tenant",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "${datasource}"
        },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(tenant_id)",
          "refId": "tenant"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(tenant_id)",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "label": "Tenant",
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Entra ID compliance overview** \u2014 built against graph2otel's `entra.*` OTLP metric namespace (see CLAUDE.md \"Metric namespaces\"). Panel queries below use the OTLP&rarr;Prometheus underscored convention (dots become underscores; counters may carry a `_total` suffix) \u2014 e.g. `entra.devices.total` &rarr; `entra_devices_total`. Exact normalization depends on your OTLP&rarr;Prometheus pipeline (Grafana Alloy / Collector config); adjust metric names to match your setup if they differ. Panels marked **P1**/**P2** read as empty on a tenant without that Entra ID license tier, and panels for a disabled/beta collector read empty until it's enabled \u2014 see graph2otel's `collectors.*.enabled` config."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Directory objects",
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": [],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Directory objects by type",
      "description": "Total directory objects (users, groups, devices, service principals, ...) grouped by object type.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (type) (entra_directory_objects_total{tenant_id=~\"$tenant\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
